  </head>
  
  <body>
    <header class="bg-dark text-white">
      <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <a class="navbar-brand text-white">EatBits</a>
          <div>
            <ul class="nav justify-content-end">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-white" href="/login">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="white" class="bi bi-box-arrow-right" viewBox="0 1 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 12.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-8a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-9a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 0 1 0v-2A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 9.5 2h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3.5v9A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 14h8a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-2a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v2z"/>
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M15.854 8.354a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 0 0-.708.708L14.293 7.5H5.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h8.793l-2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l3-3z"/>
                </svg> Log In</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-white" href="/register">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="white" class="bi bi-person-fill" viewBox="0 1 16 16">
                    <path d="M3 14s-1 0-1-1 1-4 6-4 6 3 6 4-1 1-1 1H3zm5-6a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/>
                  </svg> Sign Up</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="2500" img-fluid>
          <img src="https://popmenucloud.com/cdn-cgi/image/width%3D1200%2Cheight%3D1200%2Cfit%3Dscale-down%2Cformat%3Dauto%2Cquality%3D60/spqihfln/61016dca-0058-4150-a158-dae3008bee9e.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Food plates">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="2500" img-fluid>
          <img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/2882747.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Recipe maker">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="2500" img-fluid>
          <img src="https://c.wallhere.com/photos/52/e8/anime_girls_Genshin_Impact_Chongyun_Genshin_Impact_Xiangling_Genshin_Impact_Xingqiu_Genshin_Impact-2017907.jpg!d" class="d-block w-100" alt="Anime food stall">
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div style = "padding: 80px;">
      <h1>Welcome to EatBits!!</h1><br>
      <p>EatBits can be your go-to place when you're not sure of what you or your children's food preference are at the present time. Here we present you a wide variety of recipes that can be browsed through using meal time, cuisine or with preferred ingredients that can also be made in a fun and engaging environment with and without the help of children.
        We also give a detailed description of distinct ingredients with it's nutritional value. With the help of engaging games and quizzes, we let you know about your current tastes and possible recipes with it. We also give you numerous options in selecting a recipe you're interested in by consulting previous user reviews or based on a particular ingredient.
      </p>
      <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-3 mx-auto">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/dashboard';">Explore</button>
      </div>
      <div>
        <br><h2>Creators</h2><br>
        <div class="container text-center" style = "padding: 50px;">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <img src="images/profile1.png" class="rounded-circle" alt="Profile" width = 150 height = 150>
              <h4 class="fw-normal" style = "padding-top: 30px;">Srija Boinpalli</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <img src="images/profile2.png" class="rounded-circle" alt="Profile" width = 150 height = 150>
              <h4 class="fw-normal" style = "padding-top: 30px;">Nausheen Fathima</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <img src="images/profile3.png" class="rounded-circle" alt="Profile" width = 150 height = 150>
              <h4 class="fw-normal" style = "padding-top: 30px;">Preethi Pasunuri</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous">
